text: Eunidia strigata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fahraeus in 1872. It contains the varietas Eunidia strigata var. damarensis.BioLib.cz - Eunidia strigata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1872
title: Eunidia strigata
